      <url>/2023/02/05/termux%E8%8F%9C%E8%9B%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一.彩虹猫</p><p>1.打开termux输入↓</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">pkg</span> <span class="string">i</span> <span class="string">nyancat</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">nyancat</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>二、代码雨</p><ol><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">apt</span> <span class="string">i</span> <span class="string">cmatrix</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">cmatrix</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>三、小火车</p><ol><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">apt</span> <span class="string">update</span> <span class="string">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="string">apt</span> <span class="string">upgrade</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">apt</span> <span class="string">i</span> <span class="string">sl</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li></li></ol> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">sl</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
