    <entry>
      <title>termux远程收发短信</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/03/termux%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E6%94%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%9F%AD%E4%BF%A1/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/03/termux%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E6%94%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%9F%AD%E4%BF%A1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>⚠️⚠️⚠️注：教程转自b站up主Janwrice(up已同意转载)</p><p>up主链接：<a href="https://b23.tv/g5y9EaQ">https://b23.tv/g5y9EaQ</a></p><p>视频链接： <a href="https://b23.tv/UpJiP5r">https://b23.tv/UpJiP5r</a></p><p>0x01 安装所需应用：</p><p>Termux-API（若是MIUI系统请关掉MIUI优化！）：</p><p><a href="https://f-droid.org/en/packages/com.termux.api/">https://f-droid.org/en/packages/com.termux.api/</a></p><p>Termux内API安装命令：</p><p>​<br> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">​pk​g</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">termux-api</span> <span class="string">-y</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>0x02 为Termux及Termux API授予相应权限</p><p>请观看up主视频</p><p>视频链接：<a href="https://b23.tv/UpJiP5r">https://b23.tv/UpJiP5r</a></p><p>0x03 为Termux换源</p><p>Termux清华源换源命令：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">sed</span> <span class="string">-i</span> <span class="string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*stable main\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/apt/termux-main stable main@&#x27;</span> <span class="string">$PREFIX/etc/apt/sources.list</span> <span class="string">apt</span> <span class="string">update</span> <span class="string">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="string">apt</span> <span class="string">upgrade</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>清华源官方网站：<a href="https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/termux/">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/termux/</a></p><p>0x04 使用Termux收发短信</p><p>Termux查看短信：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">termux-sms-list</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Termux发送短信：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">termux-sms-send</span> <span class="string">-n</span> <span class="string">&#x27;目标电话&#x27;</span> <span class="string">短信内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>0x05 使用ssh远程连接Termux</p><p>Termux内ssh安装命令：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">pkg</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">openssh</span> <span class="string">-y</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对ssh设置密码：passwd</p><p>这里注意填写密码时你是看不到密码的</p><p>如果忘了设置的密码，再运行一遍passwd即可</p><p>启用ssh：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">sshd</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装ifconfig：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">pkg</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">net-tools</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看当前内网IP地址：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">ifconfig</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>连接ssh：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">ssh</span> <span class="string">目标IP</span> <span class="string">-p</span> <span class="string">目标端口</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里的端口通常是8022，如果无法确定端口，请使用nmap查找：</p><p>安装nmap：</p> <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">pkg</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">nmap</span> <span class="string">-y</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>0x06 使用cpolar对ssh进行内网穿透：</p><p>官方教程：<a href="https://www.cpolar.com/blog/how-to-install-cpolar-under-android-termux-hyper-terminal">https://www.cpolar.com/blog/how-to-install-cpolar-under-android-termux-hyper-terminal</a></p><p>对于简单的ssh，使用免费版方案即可</p><p>注意使用cpolar时它的端口号会不定时更改</p><p>可以到cpolar的官网上登录帐号并在状态条目中查看当前端口！</p><p>0x07 内网穿透也可以参考本站文章</p><p>⚠️⚠️⚠️教程转自b站up主Janwrice(up已同意转载)</p><p>up主链接：<a href="https://b23.tv/g5y9EaQ">https://b23.tv/g5y9EaQ</a></p><p>视频链接： <a href="https://b23.tv/UpJiP5r">https://b23.tv/UpJiP5r</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Termux教程 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> termux </tag>
            
            <tag> 短信 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
