    <entry>
      <title>termux搭建我的世界基岩版服务器</title>
      <link href="/2023/01/26/Termux%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%9F%BA%E5%B2%A9%E7%89%88%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/"/>
      <url>/2023/01/26/Termux%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%9F%BA%E5%B2%A9%E7%89%88%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一、基岩版服务端选择</p><p>1.小游戏服务端</p><p>Nukkitx：</p><p>官网链接：<a href="https://cloudburstmc.org/articles/?mobile=2">https://cloudburstmc.org/articles/?mobile=2</a></p><p>github：<a href="https://github.com/CloudburstMC/Nukkit">https://github.com/CloudburstMC/Nukkit</a></p><p>2.生存服服务端</p><p>pnx：</p><p>官网链接：<a href="https://www.mcbbs.net/plugin.php?id=link_redirect&target=http://www.powernukkitx.cn/">https://www.mcbbs.net/plugin.php?id=link_redirect&amp;target=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.powernukkitx.cn%2F</a></p><p>github：<a href="https://github.com/PowerNukkitX/PowerNukkitX">https://github.com/PowerNukkitX/PowerNukkitX</a></p><p>二、安装环境</p> <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg i openjdk-17 -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>三、正式开始搭建</p><p>1.在手机根目录下新建文件夹(名称随意)</p><p>手机根目录如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/storage/emulated/0/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.打开termux进入你刚才创建好的文件夹内</p><p>路径如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/storage/emulated/0/你创建的文件夹名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>termux指令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /storage/emulated/0/你创建的文件夹名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>四、安装小游戏服务端</p><p>1.打开termux输入：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">安装小游戏服务端指令&#123;基岩版版本为1.17.40&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> wget https://ci.opencollab.dev/job/NukkitX/job/Nukkit/job/master/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/target/nukkit-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.给予文件夹权限：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chmod</span> +x 你创建的文件夹名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.启动服务端指令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java -jar nukkit-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>五、安装生存服服务端</p><p>1.在手机根目录下新建文件夹(名称随意)</p><p>手机根目录如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/storage/emulated/0/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.打开termux进入你刚才创建好的文件夹内</p><p>路径如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/storage/emulated/0/你创建的文件夹名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>termux指令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /storage/emulated/0/你创建的文件夹名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.安装服务端指令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://github.com/PowerNukkitX/PowerNukkitX/releases/download/1.19.50-r3/libs.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载完后解压并复制里面的内容到你创建的文件夹内，然后输入：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://github.com/PowerNukkitX/PowerNukkitX/releases/download/1.19.50-r3/powernukkitx.jar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4.启动服务端</p><p>指令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java -Dfile.encoding=UTF-8 \</span><br><span class="line">-Djansi.passthrough=<span class="literal">true</span> \</span><br><span class="line">-Dterminal.ansi=<span class="literal">true</span> \</span><br><span class="line">-XX:+UnlockExperimentalVMOptions \</span><br><span class="line">-XX:+UseG1GC \</span><br><span class="line">-XX:+UseStringDeduplication \</span><br><span class="line">-XX:+EnableJVMCI \</span><br><span class="line">--module-path=./libs/truffle-api-22.2.0.jar:./libs/graal-sdk-22.2.0.jar: \</span><br><span class="line">--add-opens java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED \</span><br><span class="line">--add-opens java.base/java.io=ALL-UNNAMED \</span><br><span class="line">-<span class="built_in">cp</span> ./powernukkitx.jar:./libs/* \</span><br><span class="line">cn.nukkit.Nukkit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>六、服务器优化和配置</p><p>自行百度解决</p>]]></content>
      
      
